<script>
import Vue from "vue";
import MainView from "./views/MainView.vue";
import VueRouter from "vue-router";

const routes = [{ path: "/", component: MainView }];

const router = new VueRouter({
  mode: "history",
  routes: routes,
});

const app = new Vue({ router });
app.mount("#app");
</script>
